{"tid":2489941,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前AV天后引退2年後近況曝　素顏無化妝！網驚：妳是誰？","createTime":"2021-04-15T09:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T10:18:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"23f1a2e0971f45d2880957bbdbd342a531fa2d40","tid":2489941,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"現年37歲的前日本AV天后吉澤明步（吉沢明歩），自2019年3月正式從AV界引退後，仍活耀於電視節目上亮相，除了開通YouTube頻道外，還正式當起了烹飪老師開設料理教室，並且相當跟上潮流錄製Podcast。最近她更在日本募資網站Campfire上，為他引退後第二本寫真集進行募資，坦言這次不會有太多性感畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111422-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111422-PH.jpg&h=2e15abf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼吉澤明步引退2年後，最近正式當起了料理老師。（圖／翻攝自吉澤明步推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111424-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111424-PH.jpg&h=c6a061b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不知是不是放下女神包袱，最近吉澤明步在社群平台推特上傳了不少素顏照，模樣與她化妝前後可以說判若兩人，完全素顏的她少了妖媚氣質，反而讓人感到零距離感。不過網友反應兩極，有人指她素顏「模樣好正」也有人直接不客氣問：「這個哪位？」讓她的素顏照一度成為熱門討論話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111430-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111430-PH.jpg&h=eddc5e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲吉澤明步募資引退後第二本寫真，雖表示不走性感路線但仍反應熱烈。（圖／翻攝自吉澤明步推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111435-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111435-PH.jpg&h=9c8bf21a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼吉澤明步貼出多張全素顏無化妝照，讓粉絲們相當訝異。（圖／翻攝自吉澤明步推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/15/3111434-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F15%2F3111434-PH.jpg&h=5d052dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即便如此她宣告封胸不再走性感路線，不過單憑著她輕熟女仍舊美貌的外型，讓她開始募資不到10日，就已獲得超過150萬日幣（約合新台幣39,7萬元）的資金，她目前在截止前設定為達400萬日圓（約合新台幣105萬元）的目標金額指日可待。"},{"pid":"548539f8c0f97ad4faf88ffabcdeb82adc3493df","tid":2489941,"uid":4811,"like":18,"dislike":12,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeEeQbeZE8nvz4j22M6EUKusV7vc31z8jpsRYrbmehuK1?filename=EVfhiDP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVfhiDP.jpg&h=ef19f50a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da36675d94fc6284ac8f7a357e2b926213b60b2c","tid":2489941,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"548539f8c0f97ad4faf88ffabcdeb82adc3493df","tid":2489941,"uid":4811,"like":18,"dislike":12,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVfhiDP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVfhiDP.jpg&h=ef19f50a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:09:07.000Z","msg":"match<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf0c8ad87358c8a68f6da8f33c51dd58d6b7e70","tid":2489941,"uid":173921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"影到個額頭咁高嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735d0342abc617b188a7fabfca7321c129ba8e65","tid":2489941,"uid":45910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"捉～緊～吉澤明步～～<br />\n坦～白～流露～～"},{"pid":"604a84682f75e0192d428a48622dd5aad4cac5de","tid":2489941,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"735d0342abc617b188a7fabfca7321c129ba8e65","tid":2489941,"uid":45910,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"捉～緊～吉澤明步～～<br />\n坦～白～流露～～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas